    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Embassy of the Republic of Korea in Nepal supported the Ministry of Health and Population (MoHP) with 57 thousand complete sets of RT-PCR test kits that comprises of VTM, RNA extractor kits and RT-PCR detection kits through Korea International Cooperation Agency (KOICA) worth USD 6.27 hundred thousand. These test kits were handed over to Ministry of Health on 3 batches (20,000 units on June 16, 2020, 20,000 units on June 20, 2020 and 17,760 units on June 4, 2021)."
